---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const CTA_CLASSES =
	'inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-indigo-400 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 hover:bg-indigo-300 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400';

const SECONDARY_BUTTON_CLASSES =
	'inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-slate-700 bg-transparent px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-900 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-slate-400';
---

<Layout
	title="Zelipt"
	description="Zelipt is an AEO/GEO agency helping brands earn AI citations in ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity and Google AI Overviews."
>
	<section class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-start">
		<div class="space-y-5 lg:col-span-7">
			<p class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-200">
				AEO / GEO Agency
			</p>

			<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-50 sm:text-5xl">Get cited by AI.</h1>
			<p class="max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-300 sm:text-lg">
				Zelipt helps B2B brands become the answer in ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, and AI Overviews. We combine
				technical cleanup, content engineering, and digital PR so your expertise is referenced (and linked) when
				people ask.
			</p>

			<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
				<a href="/#ai-visibility-audit" class={CTA_CLASSES}>Get your free audit</a>
				<a href="/#case-studies" class={SECONDARY_BUTTON_CLASSES}>See case studies</a>
			</div>

			<dl class="mt-6 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-4">
					<dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">Outcome</dt>
					<dd class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-50">More AI citations & referral traffic</dd>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-4">
					<dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">Focus</dt>
					<dd class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-50">Answers that AI can retrieve & trust</dd>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-4">
					<dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">Deliverable</dt>
					<dd class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-50">Audit + roadmap in 5 business days</dd>
				</div>
			</dl>
		</div>

		<div class="lg:col-span-5">
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-6">
				<div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
					<h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-50">What we improve</h2>
					<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-700 bg-[#0b0f14] px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-200">
						Signal engineering
					</span>
				</div>
				<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
					<li>Entity & topic coverage (so models understand what you own)</li>
					<li>Information architecture and internal linking for retrieval</li>
					<li>Authority signals, citations, and credible mentions</li>
					<li>Content formats AI actually cites (FAQs, comparisons, definitions)</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="how-it-works" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-24 space-y-6">
		<header class="space-y-2">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-50">How it works</h2>
			<p class="max-w-2xl text-slate-300">
				AEO/GEO isn’t “write blog posts and pray.” We run a tight loop: diagnose, engineer, publish, and earn
				citations.
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
				<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">01</p>
				<h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold text-slate-50">Baseline + gaps</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
					We map what AI answers today, where you’re missing, and why you’re not being cited.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
				<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">02</p>
				<h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold text-slate-50">Content + structure</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
					We build pages and modules that are easy to retrieve, attribute, and trust.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
				<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">03</p>
				<h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold text-slate-50">Authority + mentions</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
					We earn credible references so the models have reasons to cite you.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="ai-visibility-audit" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-24">
		<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-8">
			<div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-start">
				<div class="space-y-3 lg:col-span-7">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-50">Free AI Visibility Audit</h2>
					<p class="max-w-2xl text-slate-300">
						We’ll review your current visibility in AI answers and send a clear action plan. No fluff—just the
						fastest levers to earn citations.
					</p>
					<ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-300">
						<li>Citation check across key prompts for your category</li>
						<li>Content gaps + priority pages to build</li>
						<li>Authority/PR opportunities to accelerate trust</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="lg:col-span-5">
					<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-[#0b0f14] p-5">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-50">Request yours</p>
						<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300">Email us your site + what you sell.</p>
						<a
							href="mailto:hello@zelipt.com?subject=Free%20AI%20Visibility%20Audit"
							class="mt-4 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-indigo-400 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 hover:bg-indigo-300 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400"
						>
							Email hello@zelipt.com
						</a>
						<p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Response within 1 business day.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="case-studies" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-24 space-y-6">
		<header class="space-y-2">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-50">Case Studies</h2>
			<p class="max-w-2xl text-slate-300">A few examples of what “AI visibility” looks like in practice.</p>
		</header>

		<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
				<h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-50">B2B SaaS</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Built comparison + definition pages used by AI answers.</p>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-50">Result: (placeholder)</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
				<h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-50">Services</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Improved entity clarity and structured internal linking.</p>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-50">Result: (placeholder)</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
				<h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-50">Ecommerce</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Earned credible mentions to increase trust and references.</p>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-50">Result: (placeholder)</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
